    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the exterior shows some signs of age, including minor scratches and some fading in the clear coat, the engine and transmission remain in good working order. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and plastic trim from regular use. It has been maintained consistently to ensure it remains roadworthy and dependable for its next owner.",
