    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven mechanical integrity. This specimen has been maintained to a high standard, offering a seamless blend of reliable performance and sophisticated styling. It represents an ideal acquisition for the professional seeking a balance of luxury and long-term durability. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering and experience its refined driving dynamics firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
